chart.name: Disk Metrics 24h Growth %

publishLabelOptions.displayName: instance/disk/* - Sum by sf_metric - Scale:60 - Mean(1h)
publishLabelOptions.label: A

chart.programText:
A = data('instance/disk/*', rollup='rate').sum(by=['sf_metric']).scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B - 1).scale(100).publish(label='C')

chart.description: Delta of bytes written/read to disk
chart.name: Disk I/O
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/disk/write_bytes_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('instance/disk/read_bytes_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: CPU % Trend
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/cpu/utilization').scale(100).publish(label='A')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C', enable=False)
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (A).max().publish(label='F', enable=False)

chart.name: Network Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/network/sent_bytes_count', filter=filter('instance_id', '*'), rollup='rate').scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Network Bytes In
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/network/received_bytes_count', filter=filter('instance_id', '*'), rollup='rate').scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: # Disk Operations
chart.programText:
A = data('instance/disk/read_ops_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('instance/disk/write_ops_count', rollup='latest').sum().publish(label='B')

chart.name: Total Memory
chart.programText:
C = data('system.memory.usage', filter=filter('state', 'free') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).sum().publish(label='C')
F = data('system.memory.usage', filter=filter('state', 'used') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).sum().publish(label='F')
A = data('system.memory.usage', filter=filter('state', 'buffered') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).sum().publish(label='A')
B = data('system.memory.usage', filter=filter('state', 'cached') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).sum().publish(label='B')
D = data('system.memory.usage', filter=filter('state', 'slab_reclaimable') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).sum().publish(label='D')
E = data('system.memory.usage', filter=filter('state', 'slab_unreclaimable') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).sum().publish(label='E')

chart.description: percentile distribution across all active hosts
chart.name: Network Bytes In
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.network.io.receive.total').scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Total Network Errors
chart.programText:
A = data('system.network.errors', filter=filter('direction', 'receive') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).count().publish(label='A')
B = data('system.network.errors', filter=filter('direction', 'transmit') and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).count().publish(label='B')

chart.description: percentile distribution across all active hosts
chart.name: Network Bytes Out
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.network.io.transmit.total', filter=filter('instance_id', '*')).scale(60).publish(label='A', enable=False)
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Top Mem Page Swaps/sec
chart.programText:
A = data('vmpage_io.swap.in', filter=filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine'), rollup='rate').top(count=5).mean(by=['host.name']).publish(label='A')
B = data('vmpage_io.swap.out', filter=filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine'), rollup='rate').top(count=5).mean(by=['host.name']).publish(label='B')

chart.description: percentile distribution across active hosts with agent installed
chart.name: Memory Used %
chart.programText:
A = data('memory.utilization', filter=(not filter('agent', '*')) and filter('cloud.platform', 'gcp_compute_engine')).publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).min().publish(label='B')
C = (A).percentile(pct=10).publish(label='C')
D = (A).percentile(pct=50).publish(label='D')
E = (A).percentile(pct=90).publish(label='E')
F = (A).max().publish(label='F')

chart.name: Disk Metrics 24h Change %
chart.programText:
A = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.read.total').sum().scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='A', enable=False)
B = (A).timeshift('1d').publish(label='B', enable=False)
C = (A/B-1).publish(label='C')
D = data('^gcp.gce.disk.io.write.total').sum().scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='D', enable=False)
E = (D).timeshift('1d').publish(label='E', enable=False)
F = (D/E-1).publish(label='F')
G = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.read.total').sum().scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='G', enable=False)
H = (G).timeshift('1d').publish(label='H', enable=False)
I = (G/H-1).publish(label='I')
J = data('^gcp.gce.disk.ops.write.total').sum().scale(60).mean(over='1h').publish(label='J', enable=False)
K = (J).timeshift('1d').publish(label='K', enable=False)
L = (J/K-1).publish(label='L')
